'''Sandra Nkaké''' (wavutse 15 Ugushyingo 1973) ni umukinnyi wa filime wo muri [[Kameruni]] akaba n'umuririmbyi<ref>https://www.franceinter.fr/personnes/sandra-nkake</ref>

== Ubuzima ==
Nkaké yavukiye i Yaoundé, muri [[Kameruni]] mu 1973. Afite imyaka 12, yimukiye mu [[Bufaransa]]<ref>https://www.musicinafrica.net/node/7250</ref>.  Nkaké yakundaga umuziki kuva akiri muto, cyane  Prince yavumbuye akiri ingimbi.  Icyakora, yifuzaga kuba umwarimu wicyongereza kandi yiga i Paris ahitwa Sorbonne<ref>https://www.celebsagewiki.com/sandra-nkake</ref> . Igihe yari afite imyaka 20, yerekeje ibitekerezo kuri theatre, yerekana uruhare kandi aba umukinnyi. Nkaké yagaragaye bwa mbere muri ''The Crucible'' mu 1994, iyobowe na Thomas Ledouarec. Umwaka ukurikira, yagize uruhare muri ''Le Dindon'' <ref>https://www.cameroonmagazine.com/tag/sandra-nkake/</ref>. 

Mu mwaka wa 2008, Nkaké yasohoye alubumu ye ya mbere ''Mansaadi'', ashyigikira iyi nyandiko n'ibitaramo birenga 200 ku isi, birimo ingendo muri [[Afurika]] na [[Berezile]]<ref>https://culture.tv5monde.com/musique/biographies-artistes/nkake-sandra-1492</ref>.  Yanditseho icyubahiro Donny Hathaway kuri Album ya Stéphane Belmondo ya ''2011 Ever After''<ref>http://www.rhythmpassport.com/events/lamf-sandra-nkake-cameroonfrance-2012-french-music-awards-winner/</ref> .  Muri 2012 alubumu ye ya kabiri ''Nothing for Granted'' yasohotse, yandikiranye na mugenzi we Ji Drû. Iyi alubumu yasohotse kuri label ya Jazz Village<ref>https://www.moods.digital/ja/vod/event/502/sandra-nkake-ji-dru.html</ref>. Ijwi ryerekana Nkaké ryamuteye kuba ikirangirire mu bugingo bwubufaransa. <ref>https://sandrankake.com/</ref> Yabonye igihembo cya Frank Ténot mu birori bya Victoires du Jazz muri Nyakanga 2012.  Muri Nzeri 2017, yasohoye alubumu ye ya gatatu ''Tangerine Moon Wishing'', akaba yarabonaga ko ari amateka ye bwite<ref>https://www.france24.com/fr/20181015-culture-alaffiche-musique-sandra-nkake-justin-timberlake-filthy-ngonzo-soul-hommage</ref>. 

